        <mxCell id="changes-text" value="1. Move contents up one level (app-of-apps/cluster-addons → bootstrap)&#xa;2. Update Chart.yaml name (appset-template → cluster-addons-bootstrap)&#xa;3. Remove apps/ and appsets/ subfolders (flatten structure)&#xa;4. All templates directly in templates/ (applicationset, clusters, eso)&#xa;5. Add repository-secret.yaml for GitHub credentials&#xa;6. Add root-app.yaml for root application pattern" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=12;spacingLeft=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
